      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JAGGERY (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (24.19) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and six minor placings to his credit. Can discover winning form. LADY LESLIE (1) finished second (24.13) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 8th there. Should be in this for a long way. WEBLEC WHISPER (8) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (24.22) at this track behind Zipping Olsen in a Mix 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in the finish again. SIRIUS TODD (3) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
